data.description: Beautiful Katy floorpan by AshtonWoods homes with brick front porch and extended back patio with ceiling fans.  This home features 5 bedrooms/3 full baths with the Primary and 5th bedroom on the first floor.  Gorgeous gourmet kitchen with 5 burner gas range and walk in pantry and a massive island featuring level 4 galaxy white granite.   Matching Granite throughout all bathrooms with textured linen tile.  Shaw hickory Leesburg wood flooring on main floor.  Two story living room with formal dining room, eat in kitchen with boxed tray ceiling and upstairs loft.  The Primary room features a boxed tray ceiling with beautiful wood beams. Shiplapped drop zone with shoe box, water softener and separate AC unit for cooling garage. A matching 12x8 shed and a stone fire pit in backyard.
